CEActionAmbitionsView.name: Edit ambitions
CEActionAmbitionsView.description: During the first 5 minutes after appearing in the game, you can set your character's personal ambitions.

CEActionToggleLookUp.name: Look up
CEActionToggleLookUp.description: You lift your head and look up at the sky.

CEActionVampireBite.name: Vampire bite
CEActionVampireBite.description: You suck the blood and very essence of life from your victim. (The amount of essence in each player is limited)

CEActionSpellBloodEssenceCreation.name: Form the essence of blood
CEActionSpellBloodEssenceCreation.description: You extract the essence of life stolen from other beings from your body to pass on to other vampires or use in rituals.

CEActionSpellVampireCreate.name: Turn into a lesser vampire
CEActionSpellVampireCreate.description: You turn the chosen target into a lesser vampire that must obey you. Lesser vampires cannot progress their skills without a higher vampire.

CEActionVampireScream.name: Deafening scream
CEActionVampireScream.description: You let out a powerful scream that deafens everyone nearby for a few seconds.

CEActionVampireToggleVisuals.name: Vampiric nature
CEActionVampireToggleVisuals.description: You reveal or hide your vampire nature. When you are in your revealed form, you can use more powerful abilities, but you suffer from sunlight.

CEClothingHeadBandanaAlchemist.name: alchemist's bandana
CEClothingHeadBandanaAlchemist.description: Hides your hair from chemical fumes

CEClothingHeadBeretAlchemist.name: alchemist's beret
CEClothingHeadBeretAlchemist.description: A scholarly beret worn by practitioners of the alchemical arts. The fabric seems to shimmer with traces of arcane knowledge.

CEClothingHeadBeretGuild.name: adventurer's guild beret
CEClothingHeadBeretGuild.description: A distinctive beret worn by members of the adventurer's guild.

CEClothingHeadBeretGuildBlue.name: blue guild worker's beret
CEClothingHeadBeretGuildBlue.description: A blue beret worn by workers of the adventurer's guild.

CEClothingHeadBeretGuildGreen.name: green guild worker's beret
CEClothingHeadBeretGuildGreen.description: A green beret worn by field operatives of the adventurer's guild.

CEClothingHeadBeretGuildRed.name: red guild worker's beret
CEClothingHeadBeretGuildRed.description: A red beret worn by combat specialists of the adventurer's guild.

CEClothingHeadBeretGuildYellow.name: yellow guild worker's beret
CEClothingHeadBeretGuildYellow.description: A yellow beret worn by scholars and researchers of the adventurer's guild.

CEClothingHeadBeretMercenary.name: mercenary's beret
CEClothingHeadBeretMercenary.description: A weathered beret worn by freelance mercenaries. Its worn appearance speaks of countless battles and contracts fulfilled for the highest bidder.

CEClothingHeadCapGuard.name: guard cap
CEClothingHeadCapGuard.description: Standard issue cap worn by city guards.

CEClothingHeadFedoraGuard.name: guard fedora
CEClothingHeadFedoraGuard.description: A stylish fedora worn by city guards.

CEClothingHeadFedoraTavernmaster.name: tavernmaster's fedora
CEClothingHeadFedoraTavernmaster.description: A stylish fedora worn by the tavernmaster.

CEClothingHeadFedoraHunterBlack.name: black hunter's fedora
CEClothingHeadFedoraHunterBlack.description: A sleek black fedora favored by skilled hunters.

CEClothingHeadFedoraHunterBlue.name: blue hunter's fedora
CEClothingHeadFedoraHunterBlue.description: A distinctive blue fedora worn by hunters.

CEClothingHeadFedoraHunterGreen.name: green hunter's fedora
CEClothingHeadFedoraHunterGreen.description: A forest green fedora perfect for hunters.

CEClothingHeadFedoraHunterRed.name: red hunter's fedora
CEClothingHeadFedoraHunterRed.description: A bold red fedora worn by veteran hunters.

CEClothingHeadHelmetGuard.name: guard helmet
CEClothingHeadHelmetGuard.description: A sturdy helmet worn by city guards for protection in dangerous situations.

CEClothingHeadHelmetGuardCorinthian.name: corinthian guard helmet
CEClothingHeadHelmetGuardCorinthian.description: An ornate corinthian-style helmet worn by elite city guards. Its classical design commands respect and authority.

CEClothingHeadHelmetInvestigator.name: investigator helmet
CEClothingHeadHelmetInvestigator.description: A specialized helmet worn by investigators. Designed for protection while maintaining visibility and mobility during investigations.

CEClothingHeadMetalHeadband.name: metal headband
CEClothingHeadMetalHeadband.description: A simple but effective metal headband that provides minimal protection while keeping hair out of the way.

CEClothingHeadAmanitaHelmet.name: amanita helmet
CEClothingHeadAmanitaHelmet.description: A peculiar helmet shaped like an amanita mushroom.

CEClothingHeadBowlerHat.name: bowler hat
CEClothingHeadBowlerHat.description: A classic bowler hat that exudes sophistication and old-world charm.

CEClothingHeadBowlerGoldenHat.name: golden bowler hat
CEClothingHeadBowlerGoldenHat.description: An exquisite golden bowler hat that speaks of wealth and prestige. A symbol of high society.

CEClothingHeadChristmasHat.name: christmas hat
CEClothingHeadChristmasHat.description: A festive holiday hat that brings joy and Christmas spirit wherever you go.

CEClothingHeadJestersCap.name: jester's cap
CEClothingHeadJestersCap.description: A colorful and whimsical jester's cap complete with bells. Perfect for entertaining crowds or confusing enemies.

CEClothingHeadKasaHat.name: kasa hat
CEClothingHeadKasaHat.description: A traditional wide-brimmed straw hat that provides excellent protection from sun and rain.

CEClothingHeadStrawHat.name: straw hat
CEClothingHeadStrawHat.description: A simple but practical straw hat perfect for working outdoors or casual wear.

CEClothingHeadWreath.name: wreath
CEClothingHeadWreath.description: A decorative wreath that can be worn as a crown. Made from woven branches and leaves.

CEClothingHeadTriangularGuard.name: guard triangular hat
CEClothingHeadTriangularGuard.description: A distinctive triangular hat worn by guards. Its unique shape makes it easy to identify guard personnel from a distance.

CEClothingHeadTriangularLeather.name: leather triangular hat
CEClothingHeadTriangularLeather.description: A practical triangular hat made from quality leather. Durable and weather-resistant.

CEClothingHeadTriangularLeatherGolden.name: golden leather triangular hat
CEClothingHeadTriangularLeatherGolden.description: An luxurious triangular hat made from fine leather with golden accents. A mark of high status and wealth.

CEClothingPantsBase.description: Pants to cover my thighs from the cold.

CEClothingPantsAristocratic.name: aristocratic pants
CEClothingPantsAristocratic.description: Aristocratic pants, fit for a noble.

CEClothingPantsBlue.name: blue pants
CEClothingPantsBlue.description: Simple blue pants suitable for everyday wear.

CEClothingPantsBrown.name: brown pants
CEClothingPantsBrown.description: Sturdy brown pants designed for work and travel.

CEClothingPantsGreen.name: green pants
CEClothingPantsGreen.description: Comfortable green pants that blend well with natural surroundings.

CEClothingPantsGuard.name: guard pants
CEClothingPantsGuard.description: Standard issue pants worn by city guards.

CEClothingPantsHakama.name: hakama
CEClothingPantsHakama.description: Traditional hakama trousers often worn with ceremonial outfits.

CEClothingPantsHunter.name: hunter's pants
CEClothingPantsHunter.description: Rugged pants favored by hunters for durability and mobility.

CEClothingPantsJesters.name: jester's pants
CEClothingPantsJesters.description: Colorful and playful pants worn by jesters and performers.

CEClothingPantsLoincloth.name: loincloth
CEClothingPantsLoincloth.description: Minimalist loincloth often used in traditional or tribal attire.

CEClothingPantsMercenary.name: mercenary pants
CEClothingPantsMercenary.description: Tough pants built for combat and long campaigns.

CEClothingPantsMerchantsPantaloons.name: merchant's pantaloons
CEClothingPantsMerchantsPantaloons.description: Decorative pantaloons favored by merchants and traders.

CEClothingPantsWhite.name: white pants
CEClothingPantsWhite.description: Clean white pants commonly used in formal and ceremonial outfits.

CEClothingShirtBase.description: Pleasant to the touch material, in a comfortable loose shirt shape.

CEClothingShirtDressBlack.name: black dress
CEClothingShirtDressBlack.description: A sleek black dress suitable for formal occasions.

CEClothingShirtDressBlue.name: blue dress
CEClothingShirtDressBlue.description: An elegant blue dress perfect for special events.

CEClothingShirtDressBlueOpen.name: open blue dress
CEClothingShirtDressBlueOpen.description: A stylish blue dress with an open design for a more relaxed look.

CEClothingShirtDressBlueYellow.name: blue and yellow dress
CEClothingShirtDressBlueYellow.description: A vibrant dress combining blue and yellow colors in an attractive pattern.

CEClothingShirtDressGreenBelt.name: green dress with belt
CEClothingShirtDressGreenBelt.description: A lovely green dress accented with a decorative belt.

CEClothingShirtDressGreenBelt2.name: green dress with wide belt
CEClothingShirtDressGreenBelt2.description: A charming green dress featuring a wide decorative belt.

CEClothingShirtDressLightGreen.name: light green dress
CEClothingShirtDressLightGreen.description: A delicate light green dress with a soft, flowing design.

CEClothingShirtDressMaid.name: maid dress
CEClothingShirtDressMaid.description: A classic maid uniform dress, perfect for domestic service or cosplay.

CEClothingShirtDressOpenRed.name: open red dress
CEClothingShirtDressOpenRed.description: A bold red dress with an open design that commands attention.

CEClothingShirtDressOpenYellow.name: open yellow dress
CEClothingShirtDressOpenYellow.description: A bright yellow dress with an open style for a cheerful appearance.

CEClothingShirtDressRed.name: red dress
CEClothingShirtDressRed.description: A stunning red dress that makes a bold fashion statement.

CEClothingShirtDressWhiteBlue.name: white and blue dress
CEClothingShirtDressWhiteBlue.description: An elegant dress combining white and blue in a sophisticated pattern.

CEClothingShirtDressWhiteBlue2.name: white and blue dress variant
CEClothingShirtDressWhiteBlue2.description: Another beautiful variation of white and blue dress design.

CEClothingShirtDressWhiteBrown.name: white and brown dress
CEClothingShirtDressWhiteBrown.description: A classic dress featuring white and brown earth tones.

CEClothingShirtDressWhiteBrown2.name: white and brown dress variant 2
CEClothingShirtDressWhiteBrown2.description: A refined variation of the white and brown dress style.

CEClothingShirtDressWhiteBrown3.name: white and brown dress variant 3
CEClothingShirtDressWhiteBrown3.description: A third elegant variation of the white and brown dress design.

CEClothingShirtDressWhiteCollar.name: white dress with collar
CEClothingShirtDressWhiteCollar.description: A sophisticated white dress featuring a distinctive collar design.

CEClothingShirtDressWhiteGreen.name: white and green dress
CEClothingShirtDressWhiteGreen.description: A fresh and elegant dress combining white and green colors.

CEClothingShirtDressWhiteGreenYellow.name: white, green and yellow dress
CEClothingShirtDressWhiteGreenYellow.description: A vibrant dress featuring a tricolor design of white, green, and yellow.

CEClothingShirtDressWhiteRedBlue.name: white, red and blue dress
CEClothingShirtDressWhiteRedBlue.description: A patriotic dress featuring white, red, and blue colors.

CEClothingShirtDressYellowBlue.name: yellow and blue dress
CEClothingShirtDressYellowBlue.description: A cheerful dress combining bright yellow and blue colors.

CEClothingShirtDressYellowCollar.name: yellow dress with collar
CEClothingShirtDressYellowCollar.description: A bright yellow dress featuring an elegant collar design.

CEClothingShirtDressYellowWizard.name: yellow wizard dress
CEClothingShirtDressYellowWizard.description: A mystical yellow dress with wizard-like qualities and design.

CEClothingShirtDressMerchant.name: merchant's dress
CEClothingShirtDressMerchant.description: Mysterious merchants, who had not been seen for hundreds of years, wore exactly this type of clothing.

CEClothingShirtWarriorGarb.name: warrior garb
CEClothingShirtWarriorGarb.description: A rugged and practical garment worn by warriors and fighters. Built for durability and freedom of movement in combat.

CEClothingShirtBlack.name: black shirt
CEClothingShirtBlack.description: A classic black shirt suitable for any occasion.

CEClothingShirtBlue.name: blue shirt
CEClothingShirtBlue.description: A comfortable blue shirt perfect for casual wear.

CEClothingShirtBlueCollar.name: blue shirt with collar
CEClothingShirtBlueCollar.description: A professional blue shirt featuring a distinctive collar design.

CEClothingShirtBlueGreen.name: blue and green shirt
CEClothingShirtBlueGreen.description: A vibrant shirt combining blue and green colors in an attractive pattern.

CEClothingShirtGray.name: gray shirt
CEClothingShirtGray.description: A neutral gray shirt that goes well with anything.

CEClothingShirtGreenYellow.name: green and yellow shirt
CEClothingShirtGreenYellow.description: A lively shirt featuring green and yellow colors.

CEClothingShirtJestersAttire.name: jester's attire
CEClothingShirtJestersAttire.description: A colorful and whimsical shirt worn by jesters and entertainers.

CEClothingShirtMercenary.name: mercenary shirt
CEClothingShirtMercenary.description: A rugged shirt worn by freelance mercenaries and soldiers of fortune.

CEClothingShirtOpenBlue.name: open blue shirt
CEClothingShirtOpenBlue.description: A casual blue shirt with an open style for relaxed wear.

CEClothingShirtOpenRed.name: open red shirt
CEClothingShirtOpenRed.description: A bold red shirt with an open design for a confident look.

CEClothingShirtOpenYellow.name: open yellow shirt
CEClothingShirtOpenYellow.description: A bright yellow shirt with an open style for a cheerful appearance.

CEClothingShirtPurple.name: purple shirt
CEClothingShirtPurple.description: An elegant purple shirt that stands out in any crowd.

CEClothingShirtRed.name: red shirt
CEClothingShirtRed.description: A striking red shirt that makes a bold statement.

CEClothingShirtWhite.name: white shirt
CEClothingShirtWhite.description: A clean and classic white shirt suitable for formal occasions.

CEClothingShirtWhiteBrown.name: white and brown shirt
CEClothingShirtWhiteBrown.description: A sophisticated shirt combining white and brown earth tones.

CEClothingShirtWhiteCollar.name: white shirt with collar
CEClothingShirtWhiteCollar.description: A professional white shirt featuring a prominent collar design.

CEClothingShirtYellow.name: yellow shirt
CEClothingShirtYellow.description: A bright and cheerful yellow shirt that radiates positivity.

CEClothingShirtYellowCollar.name: yellow shirt with collar
CEClothingShirtYellowCollar.description: A vibrant yellow shirt featuring an elegant collar design.

CEClothingShirtGuard.name: guard's shirt
CEClothingShirtGuard.description: The shirt worn by the imperial guard. All identical, in a single, strict style.

CEClothingShirtMerchant.name: merchant's shirt
CEClothingShirtMerchant.description: Mysterious merchants, who had not been seen for hundreds of years, wore exactly this type of clothing.

CEClothingShoesBlack.name: simple black boots
CEClothingShoesBlack.description: They won't hold moisture, but it's better than going barefoot.

CEClothingShoesAristocraticBlack.name: aristocratic black boots
CEClothingShoesAristocraticBlack.description: They're expensive enough that you don't want to go caving in them.

CEClothingShoesSandals.name: sandals
CEClothingShoesSandals.description: Sandals made of rough leather and metal fastenings

CEClothingShoesLongLeatherBoots.name: long leather boots
CEClothingShoesLongLeatherBoots.description: the perfect tool for kicking left and right

CEClothingShoesJestersRingers.name: jester's ringers
CEClothingShoesJestersRingers.description: Everyone around you should know that you exist, buddy.

CEClothingShoesPinkSlippers.name: pink slippers
CEClothingShoesPinkSlippers.description: Pink slippers made of the rarest pink llama fur. Despite its peculiar appearance, it is a very expensive shoe.

CEBaseMagicImpact.name: magic impact
CEBaseMagicImpact.description: manifestation of magical energy in the physical plane

CEArrivalsDockPointMarker.name: arrivals dock point
CEArrivalsDockPointMarker.description: Map this thing onto island map and arrivals map to indicate where arrivals shuttles should dock.

CEBaseBiomeSpawner.name: biome spawner
CEBaseBiomeSpawner.description: Spawns of various biomes on the map.

CEPaperFolderBase.name: folder
CEPaperFolderBase.description: A folder filled with some paperwork.

CEPenFeather.name: fountain pen
CEPenFeather.description: A sharp clipped feather of a bird, adapted as a writing implement.

CEBookTieflingGambit.name: Tiefling's Gambit
CEBookTieflingGambit.description: Rules for gambling with dice, created by Callista Zyanur.

CEBookPantheonGodsSileita.name: Pantheon of Gods of Sileita
CEBookPantheonGodsSileita.description: Description of the gods of our world, Sileita, may they bless our existence forever and ever.

CEBookPantheonGodsSileitaImitators.name: Pantheon of Gods of Sileita - Imitators of the Gods
CEBookPantheonGodsSileitaImitators.description: An addition to the main part of the book, which they did not wish to include in the general edition.

CEBookRandom.description: Each book is unique! What is hidden in this one?

CEWheat.name: wheat bushel
CEWheat.description: You have the choice of either planting the grains again or grinding them into flour.

CECotton.name: cotton
CECotton.description: A plant raw fiber used to make cotton fabric.

CEFoodPumpkinSlice.name: pumpkin slice
CEFoodPumpkinSlice.description: Sliced pumpkin, ready to be cooked or eaten raw.

CEFoodCucumberSlice.name: cucumber slice
CEFoodCucumberSlice.description: An evenly cut cucumber, still as green and watery.

CEFoodTomatoesSlice.name: tomato slice
CEFoodTomatoesSlice.description: Thin red tomato slice. It's no longer as nice to throw at people as whole tomatoes.

CEFoodApple.name: apple
CEFoodApple.description: A fruit for lovers of a quick snack.

CEFoodAppleSlice.name: apple slice
CEFoodAppleSlice.description: Small slices to eat at one time.

CEFoodOnion.name: onion
CEFoodOnion.description: If you eat too much, you can cry tears of joy.

CEFoodOnionSlice.name: onion ring
CEFoodOnionSlice.description: A more tolerable and easy to eat onion ring.

CEFoodSunflowerHead.name: sunflower head
CEFoodSunflowerHead.description: A cut flower from a cheerful, sun-loving plant. Inside are lots of delicious seeds.

CEBowlBase.description: This is your bowl for a delicious soups!

CEFoodPiePieceTrash.name: a piece of disgusting pie
CEFoodPiePieceTrash.description: On the outside, it looked appealing and delicious, but on the inside, it was simply awful.

CEPlateBase.description: This is your plate for a delicious meal!

CECandle.name: candle
CECandle.description: A thin wick threaded through fat.

CECandelabra.name: candelabra
CECandelabra.description: Several candles, beautifully placed on a metal support.

CEAsh1.name: ash
CEAsh1.description: It used to be something that could be interesting and useful, now it's not.

CEIronBar1.name: iron bar
CEIronBar1.description: A heavy piece of refined iron

CEBrassBar1.name: brass bar
CEBrassBar1.description: The secret of how this metal is made has been lost over time, but that only makes it more valuable: it's the only metal that can isolate arcane energy, and without it, most modern tech wouldn't be possible.

CEFloorTileItemBase.name: carpet
CEFloorTileItemBase.description: Rolled up carpet for easy transport.

CECoinSilver1.name: silver coin
CECoinSilver1.description: A valuable coin made from a precisely calibrated silver alloy... and something else. Equal in value to ten coppers.

CECoinGold1.name: gold coin
CECoinGold1.description: A gold, big, beautiful coin. Valuable enough to be stolen by bandits. Equal in value to ten silver coins.

CECoinPlatinum1.name: platinum coin
CECoinPlatinum1.description: A platinum coin? It's so rare. Ten gold pieces is the price of one.

CEGlassSheet1.name: glass sheet
CEGlassSheet1.description: Treated quartz glass, transmits light well, and is nice to look at!

CENail1.name: nails
CENail1.description: A basic carpenter's tool that allows you to do unimaginable things with wood.

CEIronOre1.name: iron ore
CEIronOre1.description: A chunk of iron-rich ore. Can be smelted down into usable iron bars.

CEDirtBlock1.name: dirt block
CEDirtBlock1.description: A block of excellent black soil.

CESeedAppleTree.name: apple tree saplings
CESeedAppleTree.description: Apple tree saplings. Plant them to grow apple trees.

CEIronScrap1.name: iron scrap
CEIronScrap1.description: Crooked pieces of iron. Only to be melted down.

CEBrassScrap1.name: brass scrap
CEBrassScrap1.description: Crooked pieces of brass. The secret of producing this material has been lost. Only ancient ruins remain as a source of this valuable metal.

CESeedWheat.name: wheat seeds
CESeedWheat.description: Small wheat seeds. What will you do with them? Grind them into flour, or plant them again?

CESeedPumpkin.name: pumpkin seeds
CESeedPumpkin.description: Pumpkin seeds. Some pumpkin seems to have been gutted and butchered.

CESeedCucumber.name: cucumber seeds
CESeedCucumber.description: Are cucumber seeds. You know what to do with them.

CESeedTomato.name: tomato seeds
CESeedTomato.description: It looks like powder! They're so small, these seeds.

CESeedPepper.name: pepper seeds
CESeedPepper.description: Pepper seeds, with a peppercorn inside.

CESeedCotton.name: cotton seeds
CESeedCotton.description: Cotton seeds. It's time to grow some pants!

CEFloorTileBase.description: Makes the floor more pleasant for your feet. And your eyes.

CEFloorTileGrassBagBase.description: A bag of grass seed. A pinch of natural magic and the dirt is covered with a beautiful lawn in the blink of an eye!

CETradeContractHomeDecor.description: Trading contract with the "Cozy House" store. Allows you to buy various decorations and nice things to furnish your home.

CETradeContractHorticulture.description: Trading contract with "Horticulture Consortium". Allows you to purchase seeds, plants and gardening tools.

CETradeContractTailors.description: Trading contract with the "Silk & Needle Tailors Guild". Allows you to purchase fabrics, clothing and tailoring tools.

CETradeContractGuard.description: Access to trade with the personal warehouse of the imperial guard. Must not fall into the wrong hands!

CEWoodLog.name: wooden log
CEWoodLog.description: A piece of unprocessed wood. Good material for building, or starting a fire.

CEBaseKeyRing.name: key ring
CEBaseKeyRing.description: Allows you to comfortably store a large number of keys in one place.

CEWallet.name: wallet
CEWallet.description: A small wallet, handy for storing coins.

CECrowbar.name: crowbar
CECrowbar.description: A sturdy iron crowbar, useful for prying things open.

CEFork.name: fork
CEFork.description: Thousands of years of progress, and there it is, the fork.

CESpoon.name: spoon
CESpoon.description: It is considered the first tool for eating, not counting the hands.

CEWeaponDaggerIron.name: iron dagger
CEWeaponDaggerIron.description: A standard dagger made of iron.

CEWeaponDaggerHatchet.name: hatchet
CEWeaponDaggerHatchet.description: A small hatchet, commonly used as a kitchen utensil for preparing food.

CEWeaponDaggerSickle.name: sickle
CEWeaponDaggerSickle.description: A curved blade used for harvesting crops, but can be deadly in skilled hands.

CEWeaponHammerIron.name: iron hammer
CEWeaponHammerIron.description: A standard hammer made of iron.

CEInstrumentFlute.name: flute
CEInstrumentFlute.description: A compact musical wind instrument, popular in villages as well as with large musical troupes.

CEInstrumentLyra.name: lyra
CEInstrumentLyra.description: A common stringed instrument throughout Sylate, popular with various bards and musical troupes.

CEInstrumentGuitarSkeleton.name: skelute
CEInstrumentGuitarSkeleton.description: A true weapon for brutal rock skeletons. What does "rock" mean?

CEWeaponPickaxeIron.name: iron pickaxe
CEWeaponPickaxeIron.description: A sturdy iron pickaxe, perfect for mining and not for combat.

CERope.name: rope
CERope.description: Multifunctional rope. You can tie something with it. Or someone.

CEScrewdriver.name: screwdriver
CEScrewdriver.description: Industrial grade torque in a small screwdriving package.

CEWeaponShovelIron.name: iron shovel
CEWeaponShovelIron.description: A sturdy iron shovel, perfect for digging and not for combat.

CEFryingPan.name: frying pan
CEFryingPan.description: You can always watch three things: how fire burns, how water flows, and how delicious meat is cooked.

CEPlatePie.name: pie plate
CEPlatePie.description: A mould for making a delicious pie.

CEBaseLockpick.name: iron lockpick
CEBaseLockpick.description: A thief's tool that, with proper skill and skill, allows you to pick any lock.

CEKeyFile.name: key file
CEKeyFile.description: A file, ideal for sharpening keys, and reshaping them.

CEBaseLock.name: lock
CEBaseLock.description: A small device customized only for a specific key shape. Attach it to doors or chests that have no lock and feel the spirit of security.

CEBaseKey.name: key
CEBaseKey.description: A small, intricate piece of metal that opens some locks. Don't give it to anyone!

CEBaseFenceBig.name: big fence
CEBaseFenceBig.description: You definitely need a towel to get to the other side

CEBaseFenceGateBig.name: fence big gate
CEBaseFenceGateBig.description: Big man-sized gates. What's your next move?

CEBaseFence.name: fence
CEBaseFence.description: A low fence restricting movement in a purely nominal way.

CEBaseFenceWindow.name: fence window
CEBaseFenceWindow.description: You can slip an object in here, but you sure as hell can't fit through.

CEBaseFenceGate.name: fence gate
CEBaseFenceGate.description: You have two paths. You can open the door like a normal person, or you can climb over the door like a funny person.

CEZLevelLadderBase.name: stairs
CEZLevelLadderBase.description: Be careful, the higher you ascend, the more painful the fall.

CEZLevelsLadderRoofRedBase.name: roof tile
CEZLevelsLadderRoofRedBase.description: Red tiles, for covering building roofs.

CEBaseThinWindow.name: thin window
CEBaseThinWindow.description: A narrow window that provides visibility while maintaining structure.

CEBaseThinWindowDoor.name: thin window door
CEBaseThinWindowDoor.description: Thin window doors. What's your next move?

CEBaseWall.name: wall
CEBaseWall.description: Sturdy enough to cover you from threats or cold winds.

CEBaseWallFrame.description: This wall is now in an indeterminate state between existence and non-existence.

CEWallIronCore.name: iron ore core
CEWallIronCore.description: An extremely hard and iron-rich ore core. You can certainly break it with a pickaxe, but it's better to use some kind of automatic drill...

CEWallCrystalCore.name: energy crystal core
CEWallCrystalCore.description: A core made of concentrated arcane energy crystals. It's extremely dangerous and can only be mined with specialized equipment.

CEWallInvinsible.name: invinsible barrier
CEWallInvinsible.description: invinsible and indestructible wall for admemes.

CEWallStone.name: rock
CEWallStone.description: A solid stone natural wall. It has a cave-like coldness to it.

CEWallStoneIndestructable.name: dense rock
CEWallStoneIndestructable.description: An extremely durable stone. Your tools don't seem to be enough to break through it.

CEWallDirt.name: earth wall
CEWallDirt.description: A tall pile of dirt. Can a house be built from it?

CEWallSnow.name: snow wall
CEWallSnow.description: A tall pile of snow. Can a house be built from it?

CEBaseWindowFrame.description: Provides a nice breeze. The gap looks big enough to climb through.

CEBaseWindowFrameBroken.description: Broken window. You can get in, but the sharp splinters will tear your skin.

CECashConverter.name: cash converter
CECashConverter.description: A simple magical device connected by small portals to the empire's central bank. It allows you to convert coins between denominations, and doesn't even charge interest! That's generous.

CETableWooden.name: wooden table
CETableWooden.description: A simple table made of boards.

CETableWoodenMetallic.name: wooden reinforced table
CETableWoodenMetallic.description: A simple table made of boards, with metal border reinforcements.

CETableWoodenMetallicCounter.name: wooden reinforced counter
CETableWoodenMetallicCounter.description: A simple counter made of boards, with metal border reinforcements.

CETableWoodenRound.name: round wooden table
CETableWoodenRound.description: A simple table made of boards.

CEWallmountBarShelf.name: bar shelf
CEWallmountBarShelf.description: Wall shelves to store your wine collection

CEWallmountKeyRack.name: key rack
CEWallmountKeyRack.description: Wooden wall board with slots for keys.

CEShuttleWingBase.name: airship wing
CEShuttleWingBase.description: Giant webbed wings, capable, along with magic, of holding the heaviest objects in the air.

CETradingSellingPlatform.name: selling dimensional platform
CETradingSellingPlatform.description: Allows you to sell any items and structures to the outside world. Fill the platform completely with mana to sell whatever you place on it.

CEWallLightBase.name: wall lamp
CEWallLightBase.description: A light fixture. Draws power and produces light.

CEPipeBrassBigValve.name: pipe valve
CEPipeBrassBigValve.description: A valve installed on a brass pipe, allowing for the regulation of arcane energy flow through the pipe.

CEPipeBrassBigBroken.description: Damaged brass pipe. The arcane energy flowing through them will flow here and may pose a serious danger to creatures susceptible to magic.

CEPipeBrassBigDelayer.name: pipe delayer
CEPipeBrassBigDelayer.description: A small valve installed on the pipe allows the incoming energy to be delayed for a short period of time. Useful for controlling the timing of energy supply.

CEPipeBrassMediumBase.description: Insulated brass pipe with iron supports. A standardized method of transmitting arcane energy over long distances. However, any holes or cracks can lead to energy leakage and harm to surrounding creatures susceptible to magic.

CEPipeBrassMediumValve.name: small valve
CEPipeBrassMediumValve.description: A valve installed on a brass pipe, allowing for the regulation of arcane energy flow through the pipe.

CEPipeBrassMediumBroken.description: Damaged brass pipe. The arcane energy flowing through them will flow here and may pose a serious danger to creatures susceptible to magic.

CEPipeBrassMediumDelayer.name: small pipe delayer
CEPipeBrassMediumDelayer.description: A small valve installed on the pipe allows the incoming energy to be delayed for a short period of time. Useful for controlling the timing of energy supply.

CEWorkbenchVampire.name: vampire power point
CEWorkbenchVampire.description: A table imbued with vampire magic, allowing you to create items of dark arts.

CEVampireClanHeartBase.name: heart of vampire clan
CEVampireClanHeartBase.description: The source of power for the vampire clan. By gathering the life force of its victims, the clan becomes stronger.

CEVampireClanHeartFrame.name: clan heart frame
CEVampireClanHeartFrame.description: A majestic artifact of vampire culture. Unfinished.

CEVampireStoneAltar.name: bloody altar
CEVampireStoneAltar.description: A gruesome stone altar splattered with blood. Doubles the amount of blood essence extracted from vampire victims.

CECrystalGrowths.name: crystalline growths
CECrystalGrowths.description: Crystallized magical energy that appears in places with high concentrations of mana. Can be used as a one-time source of energy.

CEFloorCrystal.name: crystal growths
CEFloorCrystal.description: Crystallized magical energy that appears in places with high concentrations of mana. Can be used as a one-time source of energy.

CEBaseRock.name: rock
CEBaseRock.description: A piece of rock. Hard, heavy, useless.

CEBaseTree.name: tree
CEBaseTree.description: Decades of life and growth, saturating the surrounding nature with fresh air.

CETradeContractApothecariesGuild.description: Trading contract with the "Apothecaries" store. Allows you to buy some medical supplies to treat the injured.

CEMagicDefib.name: Staff of Revival
CEMagicDefib.description: Works magically to make the target breath again.

CEPlastiseal.name: plastiseal
CEPlastiseal.description: A bandage net woven from afar powerful enough to remove poison and cure burn wounds.

CEGauze.name: gauze
CEGauze.description: Dense cloth gauze, to prevent valuable blood from leaking out of the body.

CEBloodpack.name: blood pack
CEBloodpack.description: Contains magical blood that is definitely not from space.

CEClothingCapeBarbarian.name: barbarian cape
CEClothingCapeBarbarian.description: A rugged cape favored by barbarians, often made from rough hides.

CEClothingCapeFur.name: fur cape
CEClothingCapeFur.description: A warm fur cape ideal for cold climates.

CEClothingCapeFur2.name: fur cape variant
CEClothingCapeFur2.description: A secondary fur cape style with a different fur pattern.

CEClothingCloakBlue.name: blue cloak
CEClothingCloakBlue.description: A simple blue cloak for everyday travel and protection.

CEClothingCloakCommandant.name: commandant's cloak
CEClothingCloakCommandant.description: A stately cloak worn by high-ranking officers and commandants.

CEClothingCloakGuardCommander.name: guard commander's cloak
CEClothingCloakGuardCommander.description: A prestigious cloak worn by the guard commander, denoting authority.

CEClothingCloakTavernmaster.name: tavernmaster's cloak
CEClothingCloakTavernmaster.description: A ceremonial cloak worn by the tavernmaster, symbolizing leadership.

CEClothingCloakInsulatedMantle.name: insulated mantle
CEClothingCloakInsulatedMantle.description: An insulated mantle designed to retain heat in cold conditions.

CEClothingCloakVampireWhite.name: white vampire cloak
CEClothingCloakVampireWhite.description: An elegant white cloak favored by vampire nobility.

CEClothingCloakVampireBlue.name: blue vampire cloak
CEClothingCloakVampireBlue.description: A dark blue cloak with vampiric styling.

CEClothingCloakVampireRed.name: red vampire cloak
CEClothingCloakVampireRed.description: A crimson cloak favored by vampiric aristocracy.

CEClothingCoatFur.name: fur coat
CEClothingCoatFur.description: A luxurious fur coat made for warmth and style.

CEClothingCoatFurBrown.name: brown fur coat
CEClothingCoatFurBrown.description: A rugged brown fur coat for colder climates.

CEClothingCloakMantleAlchemist.name: alchemist's mantle
CEClothingCloakMantleAlchemist.description: A mantle worn by alchemists, often used to protect clothing from spills and reagents.

CEClothingCloakMantleInvestigator.name: investigator's mantle
CEClothingCloakMantleInvestigator.description: A practical mantle favored by investigators for its discreet appearance.

CEClothingCloakBlacksmithApron.name: blacksmith apron
CEClothingCloakBlacksmithApron.description: A heavy apron used by blacksmiths to protect against sparks and heat.

CEClothingCloakCheetahSkin.name: cheetah skin cloak
CEClothingCloakCheetahSkin.description: A wild cheetah skin cloak used for ceremonial dress or hunting.

CEClothingCloakHaori.name: haori
CEClothingCloakHaori.description: A traditional haori jacket used in formal and casual settings.

CEClothingCloakMaidApron.name: maid apron
CEClothingCloakMaidApron.description: A neatly kept apron typically worn by maids and domestic staff.

CEClothingRaincoatAlchemist.name: alchemist's raincoat
CEClothingRaincoatAlchemist.description: A protective raincoat used by alchemists to shield reagents from the weather.

CEClothingRaincoatGreen.name: green raincoat
CEClothingRaincoatGreen.description: A waterproof green raincoat for everyday use.

CEClothingRaincoatGuard.name: guard raincoat
CEClothingRaincoatGuard.description: A reinforced raincoat issued to guards for weather protection while on duty.

CEClothingRaincoatWhite.name: white raincoat
CEClothingRaincoatWhite.description: A crisp white raincoat commonly used by professionals requiring a clean appearance.

CEClothingShirtSyurkoBlack.name: black syurko
CEClothingShirtSyurkoBlack.description: A traditional syurko cloak in black.

CEClothingShirtSyurkoBlue.name: blue syurko
CEClothingShirtSyurkoBlue.description: A blue syurko cloak with distinct cultural patterns.

CEClothingShirtSyurkoGreen.name: green syurko
CEClothingShirtSyurkoGreen.description: A green syurko cloak often used in ceremonial settings.

CEClothingShirtSyurkoGuard.name: guard syurko
CEClothingShirtSyurkoGuard.description: A syurko styled for guard uniforms.

CEClothingShirtSyurkoRed.name: red syurko
CEClothingShirtSyurkoRed.description: A bright red syurko favored by certain regions.

CEClothingShirtSyurkoWhite.name: white syurko
CEClothingShirtSyurkoWhite.description: A pristine white syurko, often used for ceremonies.

CEClothingShirtSyurkoYellow.name: yellow syurko
CEClothingShirtSyurkoYellow.description: A yellow syurko that stands out in parades and festivals.

CEFoodTomatoes.name: tomatoes
CEFoodTomatoes.description: A red, juicy tomato. You just want to throw it in someone's face!

CEBloodEssence.name: blood essence
CEBloodEssence.description: The essence of life, extracted by force. Only true vampires know how to use it.

CEEnergyCrystalShard.name: energy crystal shard
CEEnergyCrystalShard.description: Crystallized magical energy that appears in places with high concentrations of mana. Can be used as a one-time source of energy.

CEManaTransferGlove.name: mana transfer glove
CEManaTransferGlove.description: A glove that allows transferring mana to and from mana-storing entities.

CEWrench.name: wrench
CEWrench.description: A common tool for assembly and disassembly. Remember: lefty latchy, righty removey.

CEGunJustice.name: Justice Revolver
CEGunJustice.description: A fast and convenient guard revolver that can be easily fired with two hands.

CEGunPeacekeeper.name: Peacekeeper
CEGunPeacekeeper.description: A low-charge energy rifle that fires a powerful repulsive beam of concentrated mana.

CEIronDoor.name: iron door
CEIronDoor.description: Well, if there's a solid iron door, there must be something valuable behind it.

CEIronDoorWindowed.name: iron windowed door
CEIronDoorWindowed.description: a solid iron door with a small window. You can look through it, of course, but it's hard to put your hand through.

CEWoodenDoor.name: wooden door
CEWoodenDoor.description: Not the most solid construction, but it's better than nothing.

CEWoodenDoorWindowed.name: wooden windowed door
CEWoodenDoorWindowed.description: Not the most solid construction, but it's better than nothing.

CEWallLeaf.name: leaf wall
CEWallLeaf.description: Dense, marginal bushes. You can climb through them, but watch out for thorny branches!

CEWallWoodenPalisade.name: palisade
CEWallWoodenPalisade.description: A wall of sharp logs. Not that it's a safe haven.

CEWindowStone.name: stone window
CEWindowStone.description: A stone wall with a glass window in it.

CEWindowWooden.name: wooden window
CEWindowWooden.description: A wooden wall with a glass window in it.

CEChairWooden.name: wooden chair
CEChairWooden.description: Made of the most common planks. Simple and effective!

CETargetStake.name: target stake
CETargetStake.description: A wooden stand on which to fix a target for firing.

CETargetEffigy.name: target effigy
CETargetEffigy.description: The target is a scarecrow for practising close combat strikes.... or magic.

CEWoodenChest.name: wooden chest
CEWoodenChest.description: A simple wooden chest for easy storage of junk.

CEWorkbench.name: workbench
CEWorkbench.description: Table for the production of various basic tools.

CECharger.name: energy charger
CECharger.description: A mechanism that allows filling with mana anything, from tools to goblins.

CEDrill.name: stationary drill
CEDrill.description: A large industrial drill capable of destroying anything with a constant supply of energy. It was designed by imperial engineers to extract particularly hard ore deposits.

CEHeater.name: heater
CEHeater.description: a mechanism that converts energy into a controlled burning flame

CERecycler.name: recycler
CERecycler.description: A large destructive machine used to extract energy from magical items by destroying them. It can also be used as a way to recycle items into basic materials.

CETradingPlatform.name: buying dimensional platform
CETradingPlatform.description: Allows you to trade with the outside world, through retail trade transactions.

CEManaCollectorBase.name: mana collector
CEManaCollectorBase.description: A structure that collects ambient magical energy from the environment and stores it for later use.

CEPipeBrassBigBase.description: Insulated brass pipe with iron supports. A standardized method of transmitting arcane energy over long distances. However, any holes or cracks can lead to energy leakage and harm to surrounding creatures susceptible to magic.

CEPlantAppleTree.name: apple tree
CEPlantAppleTree.description: A sturdy tree that bears delicious apples.

CEPlantCabbage.name: cabbage
CEPlantCabbage.description: You see a cabbage in front of you. Perhaps you were born in one.

CEPlantChanterelle.name: chanterelle
CEPlantChanterelle.description: A type of wild mushroom with a distinctive yellow color and a slightly fruity aroma.

CEPlantCotton.name: cotton
CEPlantCotton.description: In a way, you're growing future clothes.

CEPlantCucumber.name: cucumber
CEPlantCucumber.description: Don't trust people who know how to turn into pickles.

CEPlantOnion.name: onion
CEPlantOnion.description: He's so cute it brings tears to my eyes to cut him up.

CEPlantPepper.name: pepper
CEPlantPepper.description: Russian roulette. Are you hot, or are you sweet peppers?

CEPlantPotato.name: potato
CEPlantPotato.description: Some like to associate themselves with potatoes. People like that are not bad people.

CEPlantPumpkin.name: pumpkin
CEPlantPumpkin.description: Legends say there is a pumpkin king who stares into your soul through the crowns of trees.

CEPlantSunflower.name: sunflower
CEPlantSunflower.description: A tall, sun-loving plant that produces large, bright yellow flowers.

CEPlantTomatoes.name: tomatoes
CEPlantTomatoes.description: On the one hand, it's a delicious fruit. But why eat it when it's much more fun to use tomatoes as a throwing projectile?

CEPlantWheat.name: wheat
CEPlantWheat.description: Most popular crop. Unpretentious, it opens the way to an abundance of flour products.
